Package com.kicas.rp.data

Class WorldData

java.lang.Object
com.kicas.rp.data.FlagContainer
com.kicas.rp.data.WorldData
public class WorldData extends FlagContainer
Contains the data for a specific world, including the parent regions list, global flags, and transient lookup table.

    • generateLookupTable

      public void generateLookupTable​(int scale)
      Generates a new lookup table with the given scale and adds all the regions in the associated world to the lookup table. The scale value should be set depending on the average size of the regions in the world to optimize efficiency, with larger regions having a larger scale, and smaller regions a smaller scale.
      Parameters:
      scale - the lookup table scale.
